data.description: LOTS OF NEW !!! Pride of ownership! Shiny beautiful terrazzo flooring throughout home. Well kept 2 Bedroom with 1 and 1/2 baths. Updates include:  New 200A Electrical Panel 2023, Newly owned 27 Solar Panels 2022 (nothing owed)-- The electric is $30./ month (for hookup to Duke) ***** New irrigation timer & pump with 4 well points 2022 and new sod in front and on the sides of the property New Garage Door & opener 2021, 80 gal. Hot Water Tank 2021, Stackable washer & dryer 2022, All new stainless kitchen appliances 2022, Whole House- Rainsoft Water Softener 2021,  newer windows by prior owner, House wired for ADT and paid thru 12/24, Freshly painted inside with new ceiling fans, Kohler Walk-In Tub/Shower 2021. Don't miss the 5 Drawer Built-in linen shelves in hallway. All wall mounts stay. BONUS 204sf of AC'd room to entertain guests that also comes with a  wall mounted TV! Outside in your storage shed is a 7500 running watt Generator with a 110# propane tank- Lots of mounted and collapseable shelves in garage. Roof  2010, AC 2017. Plenty of parking space, in addition to the garage, in your extended driveway (fitting 4 cars in tandem) Super location - just 15 minutes to the beaches, close to Largo schools, minutes to the Largo Central Park, Library and more!   Being sold "as-is" for the sellers convenience.
